{"type": "article", "id": 33280, "title": "没地方种花？试试用木头和小杯子组成的花盆架｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-10-13T23:26:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 33903, "name": "Studio Lucidi & Pevere"}, {"id": 33904, "name": "Foscarini"}, {"id": 15070, "name": "Victorinox"}, {"id": 33905, "name": "Citybirds"}, {"id": 23655, "name": "Stephen Kenn"}, {"id": 33906, "name": "Ara Levon Thorose"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 152, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161013220439FwIr8JjH2LyDz3iY.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Tubular Group 01 by Ara Levon Thorose</h3><p>          </p><p>含有曲线元素的椅子并不少见，美国艺术家兼设计师 <a href=\"http://aralevonthorose.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ara Levon Thorose</a> 打算让线条变得更有运动感。在这套名为 <a href=\"http://aralevonthorose.com/tubular-group-01\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tubular Group 01</a> 的雕塑型座椅中，Thorose 将大量条状的氯丁橡胶粘合在一起，打造出由不同的线条动作组成的三维线条画。它们独特的造型并没有以牺牲舒适性为代价，就坐后座椅刚好可以轻触到腰背的位置，鼓励人们以直坐姿势就坐。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013161041KJ0Sp1tLY6axdHPV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013161040ABwhMJaQzfRyXpt3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685819\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013161040RsIZk24pmhBfnJHT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.678484\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013161040owae18Y3SlzEfF4r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013161040nZwv0aPGQAxh31Ey.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.388753\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Convertible Furniture Collection by Stephen Kenn</h3><p>          </p><p>著名瑞士军刀品牌维氏（<a href=\"https://www.swissarmy.com/us/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">Victorinox</a>）最近与美国 <a href=\"https://www.stephenkenn.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stephen Kenn</a> 设计工作室展开合作，将别出心裁的功能与简洁利落的风格融合在一起，推出了梯子椅（<a href=\"https://www.stephenkenn.com/product/sk-studio-partnerships-stepladder-chair/iWxsMWX5avXyrmZCp\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stepladder Chair</a>）、升降桌（<a href=\"https://www.stephenkenn.com/product/sk-studio-partnerships-convertible-desk/3G9KTgnq8qKfBJ8Fk\" rel=\"nofollow\">Convertible Desk</a>）和多功能储物柜（<a href=\"https://www.stephenkenn.com/product/sk-studio-partnerships-storage-column/XWQtvWg7bZPJbQB3k\" rel=\"nofollow\">Storage Column</a>）三款家具。梯子椅由彩钢板和高级植鞣皮革制成，只要三步就能转换成实用的梯子；储物柜由三个能够 360 度旋转的箱子构成，融合了书架、镜子和留言板的功能。你可以点击文中的产品名跳转至详情页面，售价从 1800 到 4500 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160939I8cnoSqCNPKvjHVd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160939qRr5mQ6AZj3sCwY2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160939ZarXBlsHeFP2v6dw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160939tzOZyDrbKATRcnJh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160939ch6BvMJ7E1aPlWzH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Raven by Citybirds</h3><p>          </p><p>来自立陶宛的代步工具品牌 <a href=\"http://citybirds.lt/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Citybirds</a> 在 2014 年以众筹的方式推出自己的第一代产品 Pigeon，最近由 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/ignasurvila\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ignas Survila</a> 领衔的设计团队打造了一款名为 Raven 的迭代产品，磨砂黑和亮橙的配色看上去相当时髦。采用碳纤维制成的车身重 1.6 千克，折叠后流线型的凹槽刚好能够贴合用户的肩部线条，减轻了长时间携带的不适感。在通勤的地铁上，光滑的边缘也能避免划伤他人。Citybirds 希望借此改变人们对滑板车的固有印象，让更多人愿意选择这种便捷又环保的代步方式。这是它的<a href=\"http://citybirds.lt/raven/product/raven/\" rel=\"nofollow\">预订链接</a>，售价为 299.99 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160846GISUxLqW2oOHDhzf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.295844\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610131608466zgnLFvjCxl3H5VU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645477\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160847Elypzg2UvfAWOHDo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.295844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160848wPYtCB9RcWlqVhxe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.411980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Hype by Namık Yiğit İldaş</h3><p>          </p><p>有些时候，人们更希望自己的音响能够融入居家环境当中，土耳其设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/yigitildas\" rel=\"nofollow\">Namık Yiğit İldaş</a> 这款名为 Hype 的概念设计作品就是为此打造的，木料和织布的组合看上去非常百搭。它采用了三层式的结构，顶部的木制组件不仅是它的开关还能通过转动调整音量，中间是由织物覆盖的四个扬声器，还有一个低频扬声器藏在布置底座内。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160808c0lGpseqo9u5rtxj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160808z7F8EvGmniyurfIl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160807aicsZjKX0thHM3Cz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160807DKCLrY1GW8ycwvJR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160807RLPiz05yUa1Yvc6b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160810eQzOZIwLj7yqN46f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Aplomb Large by Studio Lucidi &amp; Pevere</h3><p>          </p><p>提到混凝土制品，总摆脱不了厚重的标签，这款名为 Aplomb Large 的吊灯或许会改变你的想法。它的原型是意大利双人设计工作室 <a href=\"http://lucidipevere.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">LucidiPevere</a> 在 2013 年为灯具品牌 <a href=\"http://www.foscarini.com/us/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Foscarini</a> 设计的一款漏斗形<a href=\"http://design-milk.com/deconstruction-foscarini-aplomb/\" rel=\"nofollow\">吊灯</a>&nbsp;Aplomb，两位设计师在此基础上继续了他们此前对混凝土材质的探索，带来了以扁平为特点的新款吊灯。Aplomb Large 所使用的 LED 灯被收在巨大平整的灯罩内，使它看上去就像是一个神秘的 UFO。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160718h3zW9gOxCjT0sFYV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334724\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160715MWsCAu0cfoNwLFIO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160716oxKG6rZFSmIg87yi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160718CqMvrG0E5ORodi7P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610131607154iqk0jnupKU6tMIO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>VIVO Walls by Rocco Avallone</h3><p>          </p><p>在发现窗台和地面上已经没有足够的空间放置花盆之后，拥有工业设计背景的美国摄影师 <a href=\"http://www.roccoavallone.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rocco Avallone</a> 打起了垂直式花盆架的主意。这套名为 VIVO Walls 的花盆由造型各异的木板和回收来的试饮杯组成，由于 Avallone 一直很喜欢费城当地酿酒公司 <a href=\"http://www.artintheage.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Art In The Age</a> 提供的瓶子，公司在得知他的合作意向后同意他使用那些堆积在仓库中的小杯子。你可以从<a href=\"http://www.vivowalls.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买到这些花盆架，售价从 79.99 到 525 美金不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160652hSlTUBvungcF4j8z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160651gPq3kAtrSopGs1n6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.691250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610131606521MsiHp5BtdZA0TeV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161013160656rmsLHh0d6AGxjeOI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.747500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}